    <item>
      <title>AT&T 价值 140 亿美元的爱立信交易预示着开放电话网络</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/at-t-s-14-billion-ericsson-deal-signals-new-era-of-open-ran-networks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AT&amp;T Inc. 选择爱立信对其庞大的移动网络进行 140 亿美元的改造，标志着灵活无线技术时代的到来，该技术有望为由两家公司主导的基础设施市场带来竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/at-t-s-14-billion-ericsson-deal-signals-new-era-of-open-ran-networks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 13:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
